data.title: Background – Castlepines Equity
data.text:
Company Background

Castlepines Corporation is a consortium of various private companies and trusts that invest their and their partner’s equity in a broad range of infrastructure assets. Founded in Australia, it now also operates in Europe, the United Kingdom, North and South America, Asia, Australasia and Africa.

The founding partner and CEO of Castlepines is David Grose. David and the other directors of the company decide on Castlepines’ strategic direction and its major investment decisions.
